p: Following 2-DE ( Figure 3) and software analysis ( Figure 4, Table 1), 14 protein spots were selected and enzymatically hydrolyzed. MALDI-TOF/MS identification was performed on these 14 proteins, with 8 were successfully identified. SSP2102 and SSP3101 were Apoa1 apolipoprotein. SSP3402, SSP4401 and SSP6502 were Alb serum albumin, while SSP5103 and SSP6103 were Prdx6 uncharacterized protein ( Table 2).
